  "description": "Trefoil partially unraveling — tangle at 0.75 is high enough to feel the knot but low enough to imagine it loosening. Feedback at 0.85, medium chaos. S&H LFO on filter gives a fraying, stuttering quality. This is the sound of something harmonically rich coming apart at the seams.",
